channel.description:
This will stop players from logging in as a blank name (just pressing "login") and spawning someone at your default spawn point.

RS2LoginDecoder replace World.getWorld().load(pd) with this:
[code=java]				if (name != null && name.length() > 0 && pass != null
						&& name.length() > 0) {
					World.getWorld().load(pd);
				} else {
					PacketBuilder bldr = new PacketBuilder();
					bldr.put((byte) 11);
					pd.getSession().write(bldr.toPacket())
							.addListener(new IoFutureListener<IoFuture>() {
								@Override
								public void operationComplete(IoFuture future) {
									future.getSession().close(false);
								}
							});
				}[/code]
